<style>
  .shopify-section-group-header-group,
  .shopify-section-group-footer-group { display: none !important; }
  .sym-tour {
    --ink:#1d241d; --muted:#667064; --line:#e2e7df; --paper:#fbfcf9;
    --mist:#f1f5ef; --green:#244c2c; --deep:#183820; --gold:#a88349;
    background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); font-family:Georgia, "Times New Roman", Times, serif; line-height:1.6;
  }
  .sym-tour * { box-sizing:border-box; }
  .sym-tour img { display:block; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center center; }
  .sym-tour a { color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
  .sym-mobile-bookbar { display:none; }
  .sym-wrap { width:min(1240px, calc(100% - 40px)); margin:0 auto; }
  .sym-nav { position:sticky; top:0; z-index:30; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(36,76,44,.1); background:rgba(251,252,249,.92); backdrop-filter:blur(16px); }
  .sym-nav__inner { min-height:68px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:20px; }
  .sym-brand { color:var(--green); font-size:15px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-nav__links { display:flex; gap:22px; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; font-weight:700; }
  .sym-hero { padding:34px 0 72px; }
  .sym-hero__grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.05fr) minmax(360px,.68fr); gap:34px; align-items:start; }
  .sym-stack { display:grid; gap:18px; }
  .sym-stack__image { position:relative; aspect-ratio:4/3; overflow:hidden; border-radius:18px; background:#dce5da; }
  .sym-stack__image:first-child { aspect-ratio:4/3; }
  .sym-stack__image img { transition:transform .5s ease; }
  .sym-stack__image:hover img { transform:scale(1.025); }
  .sym-stack__label { position:absolute; left:18px; bottom:18px; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(15,30,18,.72); color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.09em; text-transform:uppercase; backdrop-filter:blur(12px); }
  .sym-book { position:sticky; top:92px; padding:26px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:18px; background:#fff; box-shadow:0 22px 60px rgba(31,53,31,.1); }
  .sym-eyebrow { color:var(--gold); font-size:11px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-title { margin:9px 0 0; color:var(--deep); font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,50px); font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-.04em; line-height:1.02; }
  .sym-subline { margin:14px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; }
  .sym-price { display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; margin:22px 0 18px; padding:16px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .sym-price span { color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-price strong { color:var(--green); font-size:28px; }
  .sym-fields { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; }
  .sym-field--wide { grid-column:1 / -1; }
  .sym-field { display:grid; gap:5px; }
  .sym-field label { color:var(--muted); font-size:10px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-field input, .sym-field select { width:100%; min-height:48px; padding:0 11px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; background:#fff; color:var(--ink); font:inherit; font-size:13px; }
  .sym-variant-list { display:grid; gap:8px; margin-top:16px; }
  .sym-variant { position:relative; }
  .sym-variant input { position:absolute; opacity:0; }
  .sym-variant span { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; padding:11px 12px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; color:var(--muted); cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; }
  .sym-variant input:checked + span { border-color:var(--green); background:#f2f7f0; color:var(--green); }
  .sym-pay { margin-top:16px; }
  .sym-pay .shopify-payment-button__button { min-height:60px !important; border-radius:10px !important; background:var(--deep) !important; color:#fff !important; font-size:14px !important; font-weight:900 !important; letter-spacing:.12em !important; text-transform:uppercase !important; box-shadow:0 14px 28px rgba(24,56,32,.2); }
  .sym-pay .shopify-payment-button__more-options { color:var(--green) !important; font-size:12px !important; }
  .sym-trust { display:grid; gap:9px; margin-top:18px; padding-top:16px; border-top:1px solid var(--line); color:#4d5b4d; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; }
  .sym-trust span { display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:flex-start; }
  .sym-trust b { color:var(--green); }
  .sym-note { margin:14px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; text-align:center; }
  .sym-transfer-link { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:48px; margin-top:16px; border:1px solid var(--green); border-radius:10px; color:var(--green) !important; font-size:11px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.1em; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-transfer-link:hover { background:#f2f7f0; }
  .sym-hotel-help { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; align-items:center; margin-top:8px; }
  .sym-hotel-help button { padding:0; border:0; background:none; color:var(--green); cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; font-size:12px; font-weight:800; text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:3px; }
  .sym-hotel-status { margin:9px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; line-height:1.45; }
  .sym-field textarea { width:100%; min-height:82px; padding:11px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; resize:vertical; background:#fff; color:var(--ink); font:inherit; font-size:13px; }
  .sym-fast-note { margin:0 0 14px; padding:10px 12px; border-radius:10px; background:#f2f7f0; color:var(--green); font-size:12px; font-weight:800; line-height:1.45; }
  .sym-optional { grid-column:1 / -1; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; background:#fff; }
  .sym-optional summary { min-height:46px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:0 11px; cursor:pointer; color:var(--green); font-size:11px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.08em; list-style:none; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-optional summary::-webkit-details-marker { display:none; }
  .sym-optional summary::after { content:"+"; font-size:20px; font-weight:500; }
  .sym-optional[open] summary::after { content:"−"; }
  .sym-optional .sym-field { padding:0 11px 11px; }
  .sym-pickup-options { display:grid; gap:8px; }
  .sym-pickup-option { position:relative; }
  .sym-pickup-option input { position:absolute; opacity:0; }
  .sym-pickup-option span { display:block; padding:11px 12px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; color:var(--muted); cursor:pointer; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.4; }
  .sym-pickup-option input:checked + span { border-color:var(--green); background:#f2f7f0; color:var(--green); }
  .sym-pickup-option strong { display:block; margin-bottom:2px; color:var(--deep); font-size:13px; }
  .sym-hotel-field[hidden] { display:none; }
  .sym-booking-summary { margin-top:14px; padding:0 14px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; background:#f5f8f3; }
  .sym-booking-summary summary { min-height:46px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; cursor:pointer; color:var(--gold); font-size:10px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.12em; list-style:none; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-booking-summary summary::-webkit-details-marker { display:none; }
  .sym-booking-summary summary::after { content:"+"; color:var(--green); font-size:18px; font-weight:500; }
  .sym-booking-summary[open] summary::after { content:"−"; }
  .sym-booking-summary__title { color:var(--gold); font-size:10px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-booking-summary dl { display:grid; grid-template-columns:72px minmax(0,1fr); gap:5px 9px; margin:0; padding:0 0 14px; color:var(--muted); font-size:12px; line-height:1.35; }
  .sym-booking-summary dt { color:var(--green); font-weight:800; }
  .sym-booking-summary dd { margin:0; }
  .sym-review-button { width:100%; min-height:48px; margin-top:14px; border:1px solid var(--green); border-radius:10px; background:#fff; color:var(--green); cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; font-size:12px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.09em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-review-status { margin:9px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; line-height:1.45; text-align:center; }
  .sym-review-status[data-ready="true"] { color:var(--green); font-weight:800; }
  .sym-section { padding:84px 0; }
  .sym-section--soft { background:var(--mist); }
  .sym-intro { max-width:700px; margin:0 auto 44px; text-align:center; }
  .sym-kicker { color:var(--gold); font-size:11px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-heading { margin:8px 0 0; color:var(--deep); font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,62px); font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-.05em; line-height:1.02; }
  .sym-intro p { margin:16px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:16px; }
  .sym-highlights { display:grid; gap:30px; }
  .sym-highlight { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; min-height:420px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:18px; background:#fff; }
  .sym-highlight:nth-child(even) .sym-highlight__media { order:2; }
  .sym-highlight__copy { display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; padding:clamp(28px,5vw,64px); }
  .sym-highlight__number { color:var(--gold); font-size:12px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.14em; }
  .sym-highlight h3 { margin:10px 0 0; font-size:clamp(34px,4vw,52px); font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-.05em; line-height:1; }
  .sym-highlight p { margin:18px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:16px; }
  .sym-itinerary { display:grid; max-width:1040px; margin:0 auto; gap:15px; }
  .sym-itinerary__item { display:grid; grid-template-columns:145px minmax(0,1fr) 235px; min-height:178px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:16px; background:#fff; }
  .sym-itinerary__time { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:20px; border-right:1px solid var(--line); color:var(--green); font-size:14px; font-weight:800; line-height:1.25; text-align:center; }
  .sym-itinerary__copy { display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; padding:24px 26px; }
  .sym-itinerary__copy h3 { margin:0; color:var(--deep); font-size:26px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-.025em; line-height:1.05; }
  .sym-itinerary__copy p { margin:10px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; }
  .sym-itinerary__media { min-height:178px; }
  .sym-itinerary__note { max-width:820px; margin:24px auto 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; text-align:center; }
  .sym-pickup { max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:18px; background:#fff; }
  .sym-pickup__copy { padding:clamp(28px,5vw,54px); }
  .sym-pickup__copy h3 { margin:8px 0 0; color:var(--deep); font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,48px); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-.04em; line-height:1.02; }
  .sym-pickup__copy p { margin:14px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:15px; }
  .sym-pickup__zones { display:grid; gap:10px; margin:22px 0 0; }
  .sym-pickup__zone { padding:13px 14px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; background:var(--paper); color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; line-height:1.45; }
  .sym-pickup__zone strong { display:block; margin-bottom:3px; color:var(--green); }
  .sym-pickup__search { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:48px; margin-top:20px; padding:0 18px; border-radius:10px; background:var(--deep); color:#fff !important; font-size:12px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; }
  .sym-pickup__fine { margin-top:14px !important; font-size:12px !important; }
  .sym-extras { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; }
  .sym-extra { overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:16px; background:#fff; }
  .sym-extra img { height:210px; }
  .sym-extra__copy { padding:20px; }
  .sym-extra h3 { margin:0; font-size:25px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-.03em; line-height:1.05; }
  .sym-extra p { margin:11px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; }
  .sym-faq { display:grid; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .sym-faq details { border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .sym-faq summary { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px; min-height:66px; cursor:pointer; color:var(--ink); font-size:15px; font-weight:800; list-style:none; }
  .sym-faq summary::-webkit-details-marker { display:none; }
  .sym-faq summary::after { content:"+"; color:var(--green); font-size:22px; }
  .sym-faq details[open] summary::after { content:"−"; }
  .sym-faq p { margin:0; padding:0 0 20px; color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; }
  .sym-footer { padding:34px 0; background:var(--deep); color:rgba(255,255,255,.72); font-size:13px; }
  .sym-footer strong { color:#fff; }
  @media (max-width:900px) {
    .sym-tour { padding-bottom:72px; }
    .sym-hero__grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .sym-stack { display:flex; gap:12px; overflow:auto; scroll-snap-type:x mandatory; }
    .sym-stack__image, .sym-stack__image:first-child { flex:0 0 86%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:4/3; scroll-snap-align:start; }
    .sym-book { position:static; order:-1; }
    .sym-mobile-bookbar { position:fixed; right:0; bottom:0; left:0; z-index:90; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto; align-items:center; gap:12px; padding:10px 14px; background:rgba(24,56,32,.97); color:#fff; box-shadow:0 -8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.18); }
    .sym-mobile-bookbar span { font-size:11px; font-weight:800; line-height:1.35; }
    .sym-mobile-bookbar a { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:44px; padding:0 15px; border-radius:8px; background:#fff; color:var(--deep) !important; font-size:11px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; }
    .sym-highlight { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .sym-highlight:nth-child(even) .sym-highlight__media { order:0; }
    .sym-highlight__media { min-height:300px; }
    .sym-itinerary__item { grid-template-columns:125px minmax(0,1fr) 190px; }
    .sym-extras { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width:560px) {
    .sym-wrap { width:min(100% - 22px,1240px); }
    .sym-nav__links { display:none; }
    .sym-hero { padding:16px 0 46px; }
    .sym-stack__image, .sym-stack__image:first-child { height:auto; aspect-ratio:4/3; border-radius:14px; }
    .sym-book { padding:19px; border-radius:14px; }
    .sym-fields { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .sym-field input, .sym-field select, .sym-field textarea { font-size:16px; }
    .sym-title { font-size:38px; }
    .sym-price { margin:16px 0 14px; padding:13px 0; }
    .sym-hotel-status { font-size:12px; }
    .sym-stack { margin-top:4px; }
    .sym-section { padding:58px 0; }
    .sym-highlight { min-height:0; border-radius:14px; }
    .sym-highlight__media { min-height:240px; }
    .sym-highlight__copy { padding:24px; }
    .sym-itinerary__item { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .sym-itinerary__time { justify-content:flex-start; padding:15px 18px 10px; border-right:0; color:var(--gold); text-align:left; }
    .sym-itinerary__copy { padding:0 18px 17px; }
    .sym-itinerary__copy h3 { font-size:24px; }
    .sym-itinerary__media { order:-1; min-height:0; aspect-ratio:4/3; }
  }
</style>

{% render 'elehub-editorial-header' %}

<div class="sym-tour">
  <div class="sym-mobile-bookbar"><span>Ready to reserve your elephant experience?</span><a href="#book">Book This Tour</a></div>
  <main>
    <section class="sym-hero">
      <div class="sym-wrap sym-hero__grid">
        <div class="sym-stack" aria-label="Tour photo gallery">
          <figure class="sym-stack__image"><img src="{{ hero_image | asset_url }}" alt="{{ display_title | escape }} elephant sanctuary landscape" width="1000" height="1200" loading="eager"><figcaption class="sym-stack__label">A sanctuary, not a show</figcaption></figure>
          <figure class="sym-stack__image"><img src="{{ feeding_image | asset_url }}" alt="{{ display_title | escape }} ethical elephant encounter" width="1000" height="900" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="sym-stack__label">Gentle encounters</figcaption></figure>
          <figure class="sym-stack__image"><img src="{{ walking_image | asset_url }}" alt="{{ display_title | escape }} natural forest habitat" width="1000" height="900" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="sym-stack__label">Freedom in nature</figcaption></figure>
          <figure class="sym-stack__image"><img src="{{ water_image | asset_url }}" alt="{{ display_title | escape }} river or jungle activity" width="1000" height="900" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="sym-stack__label">A day to remember</figcaption></figure>
        </div>

        <aside class="sym-book" id="book" aria-label="Quick booking">
          <div class="sym-eyebrow">Book direct · Official foundation rate</div>
          <h1 class="sym-title">{{ display_title | escape }}</h1>
          <p class="sym-subline">{{ location_label }} · {{ duration_label }} · No riding · No shows</p>
          <div class="sym-price"><span>From</span><strong>{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }}</strong></div>
          <p class="sym-fast-note">1-minute booking: add your contact, tour date and pickup details, then continue to secure payment.</p>

          {%- form 'product', product, id: product_form_id -%}
            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}" id="SymVariant-{{ section.id }}">
            <input type="hidden" name="properties[Selected tour]" value="{{ display_title | escape }}">
            <input type="hidden" name="properties[Pickup window]" value="{{ pickup_window }}">
            <div class="sym-fields">
              <div class="sym-field sym-field--wide"><label for="SymName-{{ section.id }}">Guest name</label><input id="SymName-{{ section.id }}" type="text" name="properties[Guest name]" autocomplete="name" required></div>
              <div class="sym-field sym-field--wide"><label for="SymDate-{{ section.id }}">Tour date</label><input id="SymDate-{{ section.id }}" type="date" name="properties[Tour date]" required></div>
              <div class="sym-field"><label for="SymPhone-{{ section.id }}">Phone number</label><input id="SymPhone-{{ section.id }}" type="tel" name="properties[Phone number]" autocomplete="tel" required></div>
              <div class="sym-field"><label for="SymEmail-{{ section.id }}">Email</label><input id="SymEmail-{{ section.id }}" type="email" name="properties[Email]" autocomplete="email" required></div>
              {% if has_bangkok_meeting_point %}
                <div class="sym-field sym-field--wide"><label>Pickup option</label><div class="sym-pickup-options"><label class="sym-pickup-option"><input type="radio" name="properties[Pickup option]" value="Bangkok hotel pickup" data-sym-pickup-option="hotel" checked><span><strong>Bangkok hotel pickup</strong>Enter your hotel or accommodation address for transfer confirmation.</span></label><label class="sym-pickup-option"><input type="radio" name="properties[Pickup option]" value="Meet at Ekkamai Bus Terminal" data-sym-pickup-option="meeting"><span><strong>Meet at Ekkamai Bus Terminal</strong>Sukhumvit Road 928, Bangkok 10110. No hotel address is required.</span></label></div></div>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="sym-field sym-field--wide sym-hotel-field" id="SymHotelField-{{ section.id }}">
                <label for="SymHotel-{{ section.id }}">Pickup hotel or address in {{ pickup_region }}</label>
                <input id="SymHotel-{{ section.id }}" type="text" name="properties[Pickup hotel or address]" list="SymHotels-{{ section.id }}" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Start typing a hotel name or enter an address" aria-describedby="SymHotelHelp-{{ section.id }}" required>
                <datalist id="SymHotels-{{ section.id }}">
                  {% render 'elephant-hotel-options', pickup_region: pickup_region %}
                </datalist>
                <p class="sym-hotel-status" id="SymHotelHelp-{{ section.id }}">Start typing to choose a common hotel. If your hotel is not listed, enter the full address for your Airbnb, villa or accommodation. Our team will contact you directly if we need to confirm the transfer arrangement.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="sym-field"><label for="SymAdults-{{ section.id }}">Adults</label><input id="SymAdults-{{ section.id }}" type="number" min="1" value="1" name="properties[Adults]"></div>
              <div class="sym-field"><label for="SymChildren-{{ section.id }}">Children</label><input id="SymChildren-{{ section.id }}" type="number" min="0" value="0" name="properties[Children]"></div>
              <details class="sym-optional"><summary>Add an optional note</summary><div class="sym-field"><label for="SymRequests-{{ section.id }}">Special requests or pickup notes</label><textarea id="SymRequests-{{ section.id }}" name="properties[Special requests or pickup notes]" placeholder="Optional: Airbnb address, villa details, dietary requests or anything our team should know"></textarea></div></details>
            </div>
            <details class="sym-booking-summary" aria-live="polite"><summary>Review booking summary</summary><dl><dt>Tour</dt><dd>{{ display_title | escape }}</dd><dt>Guest</dt><dd id="SymSummaryName-{{ section.id }}">Add your name</dd><dt>Date</dt><dd id="SymSummaryDate-{{ section.id }}">Choose a tour date</dd><dt>Pickup</dt><dd>{{ pickup_window }} · {{ pickup_region }}</dd><dt>Location</dt><dd id="SymSummaryHotel-{{ section.id }}">Add your hotel or address</dd></dl></details>
            {%- if product.variants.size > 1 -%}
              <div class="sym-variant-list" aria-label="Ticket options">
                {%- for variant in product.variants -%}
                  <label class="sym-variant"><input type="radio" name="sym_variant_{{ section.id }}" value="{{ variant.id }}" {% if variant.id == product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id %}checked{% endif %}><span><b>{{ variant.title }}</b><b>{{ variant.price | money }}</b></span></label>
                {%- endfor -%}
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
            <div class="sym-pay">{{ form | payment_button }}</div>
          {%- endform -%}

          <div class="sym-trust">
            <span><b>✓</b> Official Foundation Rate (No Middleman)</span>
            <span><b>✓</b> TripAdvisor Travelers' Choice Top 10 Winners</span>
            <span><b>✓</b> 100% Ethical & Responsible (Strictly No Riding)</span>
          </div>
          <a class="sym-transfer-link" href="#pickup-zone">View {{ pickup_region }} Hotel Pickup Area ↓</a>
          <p class="sym-note">Secure accelerated checkout. Apple Pay and express payment options appear when available on your device.</p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sym-section sym-section--soft" id="experience">
      <div class="sym-wrap">
        <div class="sym-intro"><div class="sym-kicker">The Experience</div><h2 class="sym-heading">Three moments. One unforgettable day.</h2><p>Forget a crowded checklist. Slow down, enter their world, and experience the sanctuary through its most meaningful moments.</p></div>
        <div class="sym-highlights">
          <article class="sym-highlight"><div class="sym-highlight__media"><img src="{{ feeding_image | asset_url }}" alt="Guests preparing food for rescued elephants" width="800" height="620" loading="lazy"></div><div class="sym-highlight__copy"><div class="sym-highlight__number">01 · A gentle introduction</div><h3>Greet Them with Love.</h3><p>Change into a traditional northern shirt, prepare nourishing food and herbal treats, then watch these rescued giants softly curl their trunks around a gift from your palm. There are no hooks and no punishments here.</p></div></article>
          <article class="sym-highlight"><div class="sym-highlight__media"><img src="{{ walking_image | asset_url }}" alt="Elephants freely walking through natural Thai forest" width="800" height="620" loading="lazy"></div><div class="sym-highlight__copy"><div class="sym-highlight__number">02 · Natural observation</div><h3>Walk Their Way.</h3><p>No riding. No commands. Follow their rhythm into a natural forest habitat and observe their real character, freedom and quiet intelligence.</p></div></article>
          <article class="sym-highlight"><div class="sym-highlight__media"><img src="{{ water_image | asset_url }}" alt="Refreshing river or waterfall experience in Thailand" width="800" height="620" loading="lazy"></div><div class="sym-highlight__copy"><div class="sym-highlight__number">03 · Refreshing adventure</div><h3>Splashes of Joy.</h3><p>Join the elephants near the water only when they choose to play.{% if has_rafting %} Your signature experience continues with a peaceful bamboo rafting trip along the Wang River.{% elsif has_trek %} Your expedition continues beneath a hidden jungle waterfall.{% else %} Their comfort always comes first, making every moment honest and unforced.{% endif %}</p></div></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sym-section" id="included">
      <div class="sym-wrap">
        <div class="sym-intro"><div class="sym-kicker">Thoughtfully Included</div><h2 class="sym-heading">More depth, less planning.</h2><p>Everything essential is prepared before you arrive, so you can be fully present for the day.</p></div>
        <div class="sym-extras">
          {% if has_cooking %}
            <article class="sym-extra"><img src="{{ extra_image_1 | asset_url }}" alt="Authentic Pad Thai cooking workshop at Casa de Mango" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"><div class="sym-extra__copy"><h3>Authentic Thai Cooking Workshop</h3><p>At Casa de Mango organic farm, prepare and enjoy Pad Thai using a traditional family recipe.</p></div></article>
          {% endif %}
          {% if has_trek %}
            <article class="sym-extra"><img src="{{ extra_image_3 | asset_url }}" alt="Doi Inthanon waterfall and national park trekking" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"><div class="sym-extra__copy"><h3>Doi Inthanon Expedition</h3><p>Explore cool mountain trails, Karen culture and a photogenic waterfall inside Thailand's celebrated national park.</p></div></article>
          {% elsif has_rafting %}
            <article class="sym-extra"><img src="{{ extra_image_3 | asset_url }}" alt="Bamboo rafting and waterfall adventure in Chiang Mai" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"><div class="sym-extra__copy"><h3>Wang River Bamboo Rafting</h3><p>Glide downstream on a traditional bamboo raft and cool off during a relaxed riverside adventure.</p></div></article>
          {% else %}
            <article class="sym-extra"><img src="{{ extra_image_3 | asset_url }}" alt="Natural Thai sanctuary landscape" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"><div class="sym-extra__copy"><h3>Natural Sanctuary Setting</h3><p>Spend unhurried time in a greener, quieter habitat designed around elephant wellbeing.</p></div></article>
          {% endif %}
          <article class="sym-extra"><img src="{{ extra_image_2 | asset_url }}" alt="Premium all-inclusive elephant sanctuary service" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"><div class="sym-extra__copy"><h3>All-Inclusive Care</h3><p>Accident insurance, chilled drinking water and professional photography with digital upload are included.</p></div></article>
          <article class="sym-extra"><img src="{{ hero_image | asset_url }}" alt="Responsible ethical elephant sanctuary in Thailand" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"><div class="sym-extra__copy"><h3>Elephant-Led Encounters</h3><p>Strictly no riding, no shows and no forced interaction. Their comfort determines the pace of your visit.</p></div></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sym-section sym-section--soft" id="itinerary">
      <div class="sym-wrap">
        <div class="sym-intro"><div class="sym-kicker">Your Itinerary</div><h2 class="sym-heading">Your day, step by step.</h2><p>A clear view of the journey from hotel pickup to your return, with each part of the experience paired with real sanctuary moments.</p></div>
        <div class="sym-itinerary">
          {%- for itinerary_time in itinerary_times -%}
            {%- assign itinerary_index = forloop.index0 -%}
            {%- assign itinerary_title = itinerary_titles[itinerary_index] -%}
            {%- assign itinerary_detail = itinerary_details[itinerary_index] -%}
            {%- assign itinerary_image = itinerary_images[itinerary_index] -%}
            <article class="sym-itinerary__item">
              <div class="sym-itinerary__time">{{ itinerary_time }}</div>
              <div class="sym-itinerary__copy"><h3>{{ itinerary_title }}</h3><p>{{ itinerary_detail }}</p></div>
              <div class="sym-itinerary__media"><img src="{{ itinerary_image | asset_url }}" alt="{{ itinerary_title | escape }}" width="600" height="420" loading="lazy"></div>
            </article>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
        <p class="sym-itinerary__note">Times are approximate, except for the designated pickup window. The order may adjust for traffic, weather and elephant-led pacing. Final pickup details are confirmed before your tour.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sym-section" id="pickup-zone">
      <div class="sym-wrap">
        <div class="sym-intro"><div class="sym-kicker">Hotel Transfer Guide</div><h2 class="sym-heading">Share your pickup details.</h2><p>Enter your hotel name or complete address during booking. If your pickup location needs special attention, our team will contact you directly.</p></div>
        <div class="sym-pickup">
          <div class="sym-pickup__copy">
            <div class="sym-kicker">{{ pickup_region }} Pickup Guide</div>
            <h3>Is your hotel in the transfer area?</h3>
            {% if pickup_region == 'Chiang Mai' %}
              <p>Complimentary pickup and drop-off are available for accommodation within a 5 km radius of Chiang Mai Old City.</p>
              <div class="sym-pickup__zones"><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Free pickup</strong>Hotels and accommodation within 5 km of Chiang Mai Old City.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Outside the free radius</strong>A small surcharge may apply. Contact our team before your tour so we can confirm the amount.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Private transfer</strong>A private vehicle can be arranged for 2,500 THB.</div></div>
            {% elsif pickup_region == 'Bangkok' %}
              <p>Complimentary Bangkok transfers are available from hotels in the official pickup zones below.</p>
              <div class="sym-pickup__zones"><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Zone 1</strong>Bo Bae, Khao San, Yaowarat and Sathorn.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Zone 2</strong>Phaya Thai, Huai Khwang, Sukhumvit, Lumphini, Siam, Silom and Suan Luang.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Zone 3</strong>Bang Na and Suvarnabhumi.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Outside the free zones</strong>Locations across the Chao Phraya River or outside the listed areas may use Ekkamai Bus Terminal as a meeting point or request a paid transfer.</div></div>
            {% else %}
              <p>Complimentary transfers are available from hotels in North, Central and South Pattaya.</p>
              <div class="sym-pickup__zones"><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Free pickup</strong>Hotels in North, Central and South Pattaya city areas.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Jomtien area</strong>Additional 100 THB per booking.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Nong Nooch Garden area</strong>Additional 200 THB per booking.</div><div class="sym-pickup__zone"><strong>Custom locations</strong>Other locations may be possible with an additional charge confirmed by our team.</div></div>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="sym-pickup__fine">Final pickup location and time are confirmed by our team one day before your visit. Please be ready 15 minutes before your scheduled pickup window.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sym-section" id="faq">
      <div class="sym-wrap">
        <div class="sym-intro"><div class="sym-kicker">The Fine Print</div><h2 class="sym-heading">Good to know.</h2><p>Clear answers, kept quietly out of the way until you need them.</p></div>
        <div class="sym-faq">
          <details><summary>Is this an ethical elephant sanctuary tour?</summary><p>Yes. This tour is designed around no riding, no shows and no forced interaction. Guests observe, feed or join water time only within the guide's welfare boundaries and the elephants' comfort.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Is hotel pickup included?</summary><p>Yes, hotel pickup is included inside the listed {{ pickup_region }} transfer area. Enter your hotel name or full accommodation address during booking so our team can confirm the exact arrangement.</p></details>
          <details><summary>How long is this elephant sanctuary tour?</summary><p>This is a {{ duration_label | downcase }} experience. The exact return time depends on traffic, weather and elephant-led pacing, and your final pickup details are confirmed before the tour.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Can children join this tour?</summary><p>Children can usually join, but families should review the itinerary, walking conditions and transfer time before booking. Add a note during checkout if your child needs extra support.</p></details>
          <details><summary>What is the free hotel transfer zone?</summary><p>Chiang Mai tours include round-trip air-conditioned hotel transfer within 5 km of the Old City. Chonburi tours include specified central Bangkok and Pattaya zones. We will confirm any small out-of-zone surcharge before your visit.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Can I cancel or change my booking?</summary><p>Yes. Free cancellation is available until 24 hours before your tour. Approved refunds only exclude unavoidable channel or payment processing fees.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Is the tour suitable during pregnancy?</summary><p>Please contact us before booking. We can help you choose a gentler itinerary and explain walking, river and transfer conditions clearly.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Can you prepare vegetarian food?</summary><p>Yes. Please add your dietary request during checkout or message us in advance. Vegetarian requirements are easy to accommodate.</p></details>
          <details><summary>What should I bring?</summary><p>Bring a change of clothes, swimwear or quick-dry clothing, secure sandals, sunscreen, insect repellent, a towel and personal medication.</p></details>
          <details><summary>When will I receive my free photos?</summary><p>Professional photos are digitally uploaded within 72 hours and kept for 90 days. Visit our Free Tour Photos page after your experience.</p></details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

</div>

